{"word":"ἀκοινώνητος","slug":"ἀκοινώνητος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀκοινώνητος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κοινωνέω'><el>κοινωνέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>not shared with</i> another, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <i>having no share of</i> or <i>in</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>: <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>unsocial, inhuman</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}